Draw.io (diagrams.net) Offline Assets
=====================================

This extension includes offline assets from Draw.io (diagrams.net),
originally obtained from the `drawio-offline` npm package:

  Package: drawio-offline
  Version: 14.6.12
  Author:  JGraph
  License: Apache-2.0
  Source:  https://github.com/jgraph/drawio

The full Apache-2.0 license text can be found at:
https://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0

No modifications have been made to the Draw.io runtime assets beyond
selectively copying them for offline distribution within this extension.
